---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Burnham | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Burnham. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Burnham and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:340px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(12).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 35%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Burnham</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,52px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plasterer in Burnham</h1>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">SL1 · Plastering, pebble dashing &amp; painting across Burnham and Taplow.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">About Burnham</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Suburban Berkshire with a high proportion of 1960s–80s housing — pebble dash and external render maintenance are the most common external jobs.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Burnham and the surrounding area has a high concentration of 1960s and 1970s semi-detached pebble-dashed properties — the same stock that generates consistent render repair demand across West London and Berkshire. Blown pebble dash, failed render patches, and exterior repainting are the recurring external jobs. Interior plastering and skimming during renovation are consistent domestic work.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Common problems</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">What goes wrong in Burnham's housing stock.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Blown pebble dash</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Burnham has a high concentration of 1960s–70s pebble-dashed semis. The aggregate blows from the render base in patches — needing strip-and-redash or careful patch repair.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Failed render patches</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Cavity-built postwar stock develops cracked and hollow render around window reveals and at junctions, letting water track behind the finish.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Refit re-skims</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Interior renovations leave walls patched and uneven — a full re-skim gives the flat, paint-ready surface that makes the decoration look right.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Neighbourhoods we work in</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Suburban Berkshire, heavy on postwar stock.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Burnham and neighbouring <strong>Taplow</strong> carry a high proportion of 1960s–80s housing — much of it the pebble-dashed and rendered semis that generate consistent external repair demand. The older village centre adds period properties, and the Taplow riverside brings higher-value detached homes near the Thames.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">It's a settled, owner-occupied market where render maintenance and interior renovation are the bread-and-butter work.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What homeowners ask for</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Pebble dash, render, and painting.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Pebble dash repair and re-dashing, render patch and repaint, exterior masonry painting, and interior plastering and skimming during renovation. Exterior work is scheduled for the drier months so the finish cures and adheres properly.</p>
        <p style="font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Honest assessment, fair fixed price agreed up front.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Burnham</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~25 minutes from base</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">A clear run from Harefield via Denham and the A4. Covered on planned runs with Stoke Poges and Iver.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Pebble dash specialists</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Strip-and-redash or careful patch repair to match the existing texture — we handle the area's signature finish properly.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Easy access</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Suburban plots and driveways give room for the van, materials, and scaffolding for the exterior work.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Clean, tidy, insured</h3><p style="font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Surfaces protected, site left tidy daily. Fully insured, City &amp; Guilds qualified, no subcontractors.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:0;">
  <div style="position:relative;height:clamp(300px,42vw,440px);">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(2).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.78) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.18) 55%,rgba(15,23,42,0) 100%);"></div>
    <div style="position:relative;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:0 24px 40px;box-sizing:border-box;">
      <p style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,26px);font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;max-width:600px;margin:0;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.3;">Skimmed flat and consistent — the foundation of a finish that lasts.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:48px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 18px;">Services in Burnham</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:10px;">
      <a href="/services/pebble-dashing" style="padding:14px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;" style-hover="background:#E0FAFF;border-color:#0C7BA8;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;">Pebble Dashing</span></a>
      <a href="/services/rendering" style="padding:14px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;" style-hover="background:#E0FAFF;border-color:#0C7BA8;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;">Rendering</span></a>
      <a href="/services/exterior-painting" style="padding:14px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;" style-hover="background:#E0FAFF;border-color:#0C7BA8;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;">Exterior Painting</span></a>
      <a href="/services/plastering" style="padding:14px 18px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;" style-hover="background:#E0FAFF;border-color:#0C7BA8;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:#334155;">Plastering</span></a>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:20px;"><p style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#64748B;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 12px;">Nearby</p><div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;"><a href="/areas/windsor" style="padding:6px 13px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Windsor</a><a href="/areas/stoke-poges" style="padding:6px 13px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Stoke Poges</a><a href="/areas/iver" style="padding:6px 13px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Iver</a></div></div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,36px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get a quote for work in Burnham.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:15px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 28px;">Fixed price. Based in nearby Harefield.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;"><a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a><a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:500;padding:13px 26px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a></div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
